protein.general_function: Involved in transferase activity, transferring hexosyl groups
protein.specific_function: Catalyzes the formation of some glycolipid via the addition of N-acetylgalactosamine (GalNAc) in alpha-1,3-linkage to some substrate. Glycolipids probably serve for adherence of some pathogens
